// Testimonials section - Social proof
---

<section class="testimonials" id="resultaten">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="testimonials-header">
      <span class="section-label">Resultaten</span>
      <h2>Wat klanten zeggen</h2>
      <p class="testimonials-intro">
        Geen marketing-praatjes, maar echte resultaten van echte ondernemers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card testimonial-featured">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.1">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
          </svg>
          <p>
            "Eindelijk iemand die begrijpt wat ik nodig heb zonder dat ik 
            in technisch jargon hoef te praten. Karel heeft mijn website 
            Ã©n automatiseringen opgezet. Ik bespaar nu letterlijk 10 uur 
            per week aan administratie."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">MV</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <span class="author-name">Marieke van der Berg</span>
            <span class="author-title">ZZP'er, Boekhouder</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-result">
          <span class="result-label">Resultaat:</span>
          <span class="result-value">10 uur/week bespaard</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">
          <p>
            "Mijn oude website kostte me klanten. Nu krijg ik wekelijks 
            aanvragen via de site. De investering was binnen 2 maanden 
            terugverdiend."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">JK</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <span class="author-name">Jeroen Kuiper</span>
            <span class="author-title">Eigenaar, Schildersbedrijf</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-result">
          <span class="result-label">Resultaat:</span>
          <span class="result-value">5x meer offerteaanvragen</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">
          <p>
            "Ik had een klantportaal nodig maar wist niet waar te beginnen. 
            Karel luisterde, stelde de juiste vragen, en leverde precies 
            wat ik nodig had. Topservice."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">SR</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <span class="author-name">Sandra Roos</span>
            <span class="author-title">Directeur, Consultancybureau</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-result">
          <span class="result-label">Resultaat:</span>
          <span class="result-value">Professioneler imago</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">
          <p>
            "De automatisering van mijn facturatie was een gamechanger. 
            Geen gemiste facturen meer, geen stress aan het eind van de maand. 
            Aanrader!"
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">PD</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <span class="author-name">Peter de Jong</span>
            <span class="author-title">Freelance Fotograaf</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-result">
          <span class="result-label">Resultaat:</span>
          <span class="result-value">0 gemiste facturen</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    background: var(--color-canvas-alt);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .testimonials::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-primary), transparent);
  }

  .testimonials-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .testimonials-intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .testimonial-featured {
      grid-row: span 2;
    }
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .testimonial-featured {
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-white) 0%, rgba(255, 107, 74, 0.03) 100%);
  }

  .testimonial-quote {
    position: relative;
    flex-grow: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .testimonial-quote svg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .testimonial-featured .testimonial-quote svg {
    position: static;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .testimonial-quote p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-ink-light);
  }

  .testimonial-featured .testimonial-quote p {
    font-size: 1.1875rem;
  }

  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding-top: var(--space-md);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.08);
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .author-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .author-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .author-title {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  }

  .testimonial-result {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-sm);
    background: rgba(255, 107, 74, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .result-label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  }

  .result-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
</style>
